Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:03.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:18.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你秘书说可以进来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your secretary said to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比·布里格斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 你知道\N你一生中必须要有的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, you know\Nwhat you have to have in this life?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,平衡.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:30.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,距离.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:33.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对称.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Symmetry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:41.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,多美丽啊, 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a beautiful thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:53.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩先生, 你听了我\N送来的那盒录音带了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne, did you listen\Nto that tape that l sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有, 我听过了, 波比.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l listened to your tape, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:03:00.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说, 里欧能控制一门技术\N我对此还真吓了一跳.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:03:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, l am surprised\Nthat Leo could master the technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这该死的, 波比, 你想要什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Bobby, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,荷恩先生,\N我对你万分钦佩.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Horne,\Nl have a great admiration for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,钦佩这词是给诗人和\N奶牛用的, 波比.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiration is for poets\Nand dairy cows, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:19.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很懂你的意思. 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know what you mean. l...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:29.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你正站在一幢\N庞然的摩天大楼前.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're standing in front\Nof a mammoth skyscraper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这只海怪撕开一个云洞\N正直冲凌霄.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A leviathan that rips a hole\Nin the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:36.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 第一个出现在你脑海\N里的问题是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's the first question\Nthat comes to your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:48.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你问自己的第一个问题\N就是, "在最高处的是什么?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first question that you ask yourself\Nis, ''What's on the top floor?''
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:52.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"坐在楼顶阁楼里的谁,\N为什么?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Who's up there in the penthouse,\Nand why?''
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,吶, 我是一个这样的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that's who l am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这样的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:05.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,  我当然是了. 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course l am. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:13.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 机会找上门了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, opportunity knocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:22.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你去跟踪汉克·詹宁斯.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to follow Hank Jennings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:26.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你记录\N他的生活的一切.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to chronicle\Nhis existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:30.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去展示那些\N我所不知的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me something\Nthat l don't already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2个我都想去看.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd like to see both.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:52.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很好. 那你想先看\N哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good. Which one\Nwould you like to see first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我之前把那个排除了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd thought l'd taken that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:20.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个房产\N死狗农庄.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That property\Nis called Dead Dog Farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有比这更糟的呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's worse than it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是什么?\N- 反正迷雾重重.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What is it?\N- A puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从来没人在那儿住的长久.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever really stays there long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候能去看?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When can l see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我来晚了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry l'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但那个小年轻已经对我们的\N野营之旅兴奋不已了,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the little nipper is so excited\Nabout our camping trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我实在没办法\N把他哄下车.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just couldn't coax him\Nout of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,理查, 这位是朱迪·斯温
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard, this is Judy Swain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:45.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,从快乐帮手组织\N那边过来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the Happy Helping Hands\Norganization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是小尼克的跟进人.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm little Nicky's case manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不胜荣幸, 我肯定. 那我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charmed, l'm sure. Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:53.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:58.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我准备向你朋友说的,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As l was about to tell your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:01.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,关于要了解尼克的\N第一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the number one thing\Nto know about Nicky
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:07.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他这小小年纪,\N就已经被搞的非常狼狈了,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that throughout his brief life,\Nhe has been very confused,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:13.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是因为被一连串的\N不幸事件伤害过吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and perhaps traumatized\Nby a persistent random misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来他好像被收容所\N推来让去好多次了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's bounced around\Nquite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊, 是的, 的确是这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可怜的孩子.\N- 就是.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Poor child.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吧,他是个孤儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An orphan, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗? 发生什么了?\N他父母死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What happened?\NDid his parents die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,出色的推理啊, 安德鲁.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicely deduced, Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一连串不幸事件?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent random misfortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,他们被杀害了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么被杀害的, 斯温小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How were they killed, Miss Swain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,神秘事件.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:42.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉,孤儿院从未\N向我们提供过那方面的信息.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm afraid the orphanage has never\Nprovided us with that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:46.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 我们出发吧.\N北方大酒店有突发事件.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, let's go.\NEmergency up at the Great Northern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是心脏病发.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:10.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦受到刺激,\N雌性身上的皮肤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once stimulated,\Nthe female will respond in such a way
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,会以一种这样的方式作出反应...\N噢, 我的上帝啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the skin around her...\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来杜恩这次真\N魂归天国了.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Dougie went out\Nwith his boots on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:21.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}拜伦勋爵的爱情诗集,\N爱神性经,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love Poems of Lord Byron,\NThe Kama Sutra,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}小偷与女仆.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hookers and Handmaidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警长, 开这个.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谁又在这儿闹事啦.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a falling out was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:51.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊, 我真讨厌这样说, 我早就警告过你了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord, l hate to say it, l told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看这儿, 警长.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是它.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人凶器.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:13.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她可能还用\N来复枪打爆了他的头呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might as well\Nhave blown his brains out with a rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:24.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他从来不能拒绝女色.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never could say no to a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你这老傻帽.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You old fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:53.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个色相女骗子,\N为此,你会给地狱之火烧死的.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sexual adventuress,\Nyou'll burn in hell for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:58.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别激动, 先生.\N- 我要把你数臭,直到我死为止.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Take it easy, mister.\N- l'm gonna shout till l wake the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她谋杀了我亲兄弟.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She murdered my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个恶毒的巫婆.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:07.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她是对的, 我被诅咒了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, l'm cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别犯傻了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:13.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不, 是真的.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:18.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,高中时就开始了,\N舞会之夜.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt all started in high school,\Nprom night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我舞伴来吻我.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My date went to kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:25.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他头一天\N穿这他新的吊裤带.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was his first day\Nwith his new braces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 它们在月夜中\N闪闪发光.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and they gleamed\Nin the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:34.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,之后橡皮带啪嗒断掉了\N抽的他下颚痉挛脱了韧,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his rubber band snapped\Nand his jaw locked open,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就那样\N在急救室结束了,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we ended up\Nin the emergency room,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:41.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,医生不得不打碎3处颚骨\N去重新缝合它.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the doctors had to break his jaw\Nin three places to get it to shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:46.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,打那儿时起更是每况愈下了.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's just gotten worse ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要解咒.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A curse needs a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂一些这方面的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know a bit about these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:53.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是警长吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:10:00.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说吧, 每当有真正重大\N事故降临, 我就是个男子汉.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:10:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say, when something\Nreally big goes down, l'm the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:11.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小子们, 有一个关于\N伟大足球教练的故事,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys, there's a story\Nabout a great football coach,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,名字我现在\N不记得了,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose name escapes me\Nat this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:18.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他坚决反对\N有任何黑人球员在他队里.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was dead set against\Nhaving any black players on his team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:23.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,直到某人把世界上最好的\N黑人众中卫带到他面前.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until somebody brought him the finest\Nblack halfback anyone had ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当他,他叫什么来着?\N看他跑出50码后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when what's-his-name\Nsaw him run 50 yards
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,已经无人能及时,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and no one lay a hand on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他大喊到, "看那个印第安人,牛!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he shouted, ''Look at that lndian go!''
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:37.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个教练终于接受了\N那个燃烧着竞技欲望的运动员.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That coach accepted\Nthat athlete's desire to compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳丁.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:44.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而今天, 这个故事同样适用\N于这位女士--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And today, this story applies\Nto this woman's--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这位少女适合竞技.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This young girl's right to compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:51.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,此外 这对她,不但符合道德\N也符合宪法权利.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln addition to it being her moral\Nand constitutional right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:56.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克·尼森,\N你能上前来一下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mike Nelson,\Ncould you step up here for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧, 麦克, 去吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Mike, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:05.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 纳丁已经选择了\N我们中最好的为对手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Nadine has chosen\Nto prove herself to us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:08.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来向我们证明她的实力了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by taking on our very best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:11.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真正的区冠军,\N麦克·尼森.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our very own district champion,\NMike Nelson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:14.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 呀! 来吧. 开干吧.\N- 好啊, 伙计.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah! Come on. Come on.\N- All right, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,放马去吧, 麦克.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:19.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨, 麦克.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把你手放这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 现在推抵我.\N我会尽量不伤到你.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now just push against me.\Nl'll try not to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚想出去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go out tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这招叫『系』.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called a tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦, 呀.\N- 你这笨瓜...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, yeah.\N- You stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚说什么来着, 麦克?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:47.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子, 你快把我脖子拧断了.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neck, you're breaking my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对,\N这事有点像搂抱.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right,\Nthis is sort of like necking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:56.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚到底怎样嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,教练?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 教练?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:11.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 站起来, 麦克.\N- 噢, 我的天啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get up, Mike.\N- Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:15.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2，3.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two and three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你会和我出去了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now will you go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我给一个女生痛打了一顿.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got beat up by a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你对她作了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 我不是开玩笑的.\N那, 你这回可真得帮帮我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, l'm not kidding.\NNow, you've gotta help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当着全队的面被人践踏在脚下\N已经够衰了,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's bad enough getting stomped on\Nin front of the whole team,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:48.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她还喜欢上我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁?\N- 何丽太太.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who?\N- Mrs. Hurley.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,纳丁?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nadine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:55.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好玩.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道, 或许你正需要\N一个比你大的女人.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know, maybe an older woman\Nis just what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和一个能把我熊扑在地\N的女人约会.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't wanna go out with anyone\Nwho can body-slam me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 你想我\N做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you want me\Nto do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道, 和她谈谈.\N假装你仍是我女友.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know, talk to her or something.\NPretend you're still my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思, 麦克,\N我可不是个好演员.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mike,\Nl'm not that good of an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:13.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜, 这是认真的.\N你必须拉我一把.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donna, this is serious.\Nl'm gonna end up in traction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:26.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,能帮你点什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May l help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滞留的当地武装叛军,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang up a local service rebellion,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:33.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想知道你是否愿意帮我去捡些\N柴火来烧死那个军官俘虏.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wonder if you'd help me bundle up\Nloose sticks and burn that master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:38.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马科, 马科·斯隆,\N伊夫林的弟弟.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malcolm, Malcolm Sloan,\Nas in brother to Evelyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也是玛舒先生的司机,\N"把车开进来, 詹姆斯."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Marsh's driver, as in,\N''Bring that car around, James.''
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她到底把那辆『捷豹』\N糟蹋成什么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how badly\Ndid she damage the Jag?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还是可以修的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's repairable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:49.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在某些事上还是能做点什么的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the nice thing about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗, 她和杰弗里\N共坠爱河时,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when she and Jeffrey\Nfell in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他给了她一个全新的生活.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he gave her a whole new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是理所当然的.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:04.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了一套好工作服,\N和酒柜的钥匙.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now l got a nice uniform,\Nand the keys to the liquor cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊, 我希望\N我没让你觉得不愉快,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, l hope\Nl don't sound ungrateful,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,因为比起我以前\N过的生活,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because compared\Nto the life l was living,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只是更进一步在荒废罢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wanton dissipation is a step up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:16.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而伊夫林,\N她也自己得到了很多.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Evelyn,\Nshe learned a lot herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:20.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,防卫状态,\N掩饰瘀伤, 恶性循环.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defensive postures,\Nmasking bruises, vicious cycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉, 我说的很隐晦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, am l being obscure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:28.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2个星期前,\N杰弗里毫不留情的猛打了她一顿,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once a fortnight,\NJeffrey pounds her mercilessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而她就想打烂他一件宝贝\N来报复他.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she tries to get even\Nby breaking one of his things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样没完没了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt only perpetuates the cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:38.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你姐姐.\N你怎么不制止他?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's your sister.\NWhy don't you stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:44.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,小乖乖,\N没人能制止玛舒先生.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonny boy,\Nnobody stops Mr. Marsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:47.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是这儿的金科玉律.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a golden rule around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把它记下来\N塞在枕头底下.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can jot that down\Nand put it under your pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l gotta get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 谢谢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真得.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:35.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哇, 它还在那儿好好的呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's still standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没怎么变过.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost by force of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:41.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 不变提供了\N一个坚实的基础.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, habit can provide\Na strong foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,死狗农庄, 呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead Dog Farm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个老传说.\N这世界上的所有人,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an old legend.\NOf all the people in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:49.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,最优秀的和最差劲的\N都被死狗吸引而来,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the best and the worst\Nare drawn to Dead Dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后有几乎全都给吓跑了.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and most turn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只有那些最纯净的心灵\N能感受到它的痛苦.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those with the purest of heart\Ncan feel its pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:16:00.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有某个角落夹缝里,\N我们的终身挣扎和奋斗史.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:16:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And somewhere in between,\Nthe rest of us struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伊伦, 你最近还带过其他人来看\N这房产吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lrene, have you shown this property\Nto anyone else recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:07.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去年就已经没人\N再来看了.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't think anyone's asked\Nto see it this last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:09.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有3台车来过这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's three vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:13.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一辆吉普车, 一辆4驱车\N还有一辆豪华轿车.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A jeep, a four-wheeler\Nand a luxury sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,门开着呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有人么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:34.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在这碰过头.\N几小时前的事.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a meeting here.\Nln the past few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们忘了\N这儿是没有自来水的.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They forgot\Nthere was no running water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是婴儿泻药.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby laxative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多白粉末.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More white powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可卡因.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:50.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,伊伦, 我们得通知警长了.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lrene, we have to notify the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尼克, 请停止.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicky, stop that, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:17.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尼克, 停止.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicky, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就看不懂.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't understand this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just had the car checked\Nat Gas Farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他还告诉我\N它运行的极好呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me it was\Nin perfect working order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:31.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,运行的极好呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect working order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:37.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这都太技术化了.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all so technical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:45.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了, 尼克,\N基巴叔叔正在读说明书呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Nicky,\NUncle Dick is trying to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尼古拉斯, 滚下车!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicholas, get out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尼古拉斯, 快给我滚下车, 马上!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicholas, out of the car, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:03.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,滚下车!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.19,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在生我气吗, 基巴叔叔?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad at me, Uncle Dick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:15.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 我当然没有生你气.\N我为什么要生你气呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course l'm not mad at you.\NWhy should l be mad at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我吓着你了, 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scared you, didn't l?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,基巴叔叔!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:49.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别怕, 别怕,\N我没事, 小尼克.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, don't worry,\Nl'm all right, little Nicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:53.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你死了怎么办?\N你不会死的, 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you died?\NYou aren't gonna die, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:57.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然不会. 别说傻话了.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库珀. 这位是莱利上校.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper. This is Colonel Riley.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他是空军派来\N调查布里格斯失踪案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's heading up\Nthe Air Force's investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的负责人.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into Briggs' disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 上校.\N- 库珀.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Colonel.\N- Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:15.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当我们失去布里格斯的坐标时\N你正和他在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were with Briggs\Nwhen we lost our coordinates on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 我在.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:21.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里,\N你注意到有任何野生动物出现吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were at the site,\Ndid you notice any wildlife in the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 野生动物?\N- 鸟, 猫头鹰?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wildlife?\N- Birds, owls?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有, 就在少校消失的\N那一刻, 我听见一只猫头鹰叫.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just moments before the major\Ndisappeared, l heard an owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还看到什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any visual contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看, 上校, 加兰·布里格斯\N是我的好朋友.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, colonel, Garland Briggs\Nis a good friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么你不妨对我们直说\N不更好吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would be a lot better\Nif you'd just level with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:42.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道监视器\N和来自外层空间的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know about the monitors\Nand the messages from deep space
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以及你接收到有关于我的那个.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you received pertaining to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:49.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你或许知道一些事情,\N但你最好还是先搞清楚其他的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may know something,\Nbut you best get your facts straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:52.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的监视器指向\N外太空,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our monitors are pointed\Nat deep space,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:57.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但布里格斯给你看\N我们截获的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the messages we intercepted\Nthat Briggs showed you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:21:01.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这树林里\N被发出去的.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were sent from right here\Nin these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:05.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 它们被发送到哪儿去\N就是另一个问题了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where they were sent to\Nis another question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:10.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,发生的这些事大概和一个\N叫守日门的地方有关吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might this have something to do\Nwith a place called the White Lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:12.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是高度机密.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上校, 我们很愿意帮助你,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, we'd like to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但你要让我们知道更多一些\N这才能继续下去.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you need to give us\Na little more to go on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:24.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰·布里格斯是我所认识的\N最好的飞行员.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland Briggs is the best pilot\Nl've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:29.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他天生是块料子\N而我们大多数人只能梦想.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was born with hardware\Nmost of us only dream about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:31.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以告诉你这个:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:38.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他的消失所带来的暗示\N已经远远超出了国家安全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His disappearance has implications\Nthat go so far beyond national security
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:42.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,冷战似乎\N一触即发的状态了.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Cold War seems like a case\Nof the sniffles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:55.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎很好,\N车轴应该还行.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The engine's fine,\Nthe axle should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么对这个这么在行?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get so good at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:01.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 我叔叔艾德教的.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my uncle Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我在行,\N那你应该见见他.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think l'm good,\Nyou should see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他什么都能修.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can fix anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:11.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天和你弟弟聊过了\N他讲了一些你的情况.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was talking to your brother today\Na little bit about your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:14.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看, 詹姆斯,\N少管闲事.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, James,\Nmind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:18.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:20.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕你的丈夫么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:26.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这么什么好说的.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:31.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解什么是孤独的滋味.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know what it's like to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:50.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕他, 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.61,0:22:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are afraid of him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:54.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你不离开?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.23,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没那么简单.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.35,0:22:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 我的天啊, 他回来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:14.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,事情没有那么坏.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not as bad as l made it out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:52.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 看谁来了.\N爸爸改变主意了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.27,0:23:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look who's here.\NDid Daddy have a change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:55.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸只是做了这些年来\N最明智的决定而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy just made the smartest decision\Nthat he's made all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:59.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 真的? 那不能说明什么.\N他做了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? That's not saying much.\NWhat did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:01.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,工资单上有我的名字了.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He put me on the payroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:05.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 你是3年班的成功人士了, 好家伙你.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, you junior achiever, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:06.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.52,0:24:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:09.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的首个任务.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.03,0:24:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:12.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么我可以帮助你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything l can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.92,0:24:14.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.53,0:24:19.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或许你帮我庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can help me celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.07,0:24:22.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在我给老板看了这个之后.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.37,0:24:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after l show this to the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:25.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 你知道我怎么想的,\N波比·布里格斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know what l think,\NBobby Briggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.46,0:24:26.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.08,0:24:30.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想我们应该想想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.38,0:24:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think that we should think
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.95,0:24:35.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起搞点什么生意.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.25,0:24:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about doing business together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.01,0:24:44.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 你这个点子不错.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.29,0:24:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, l like the way you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.28,0:24:45.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.60,0:24:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.67,0:25:10.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿, 荷恩先生, 过的还好?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.99,0:25:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Horne, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.98,0:25:18.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其实，你这是\N在这干嘛呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.29,0:25:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this\Nyou're doing here, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.69,0:25:22.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,盖茨堡, 第一天.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gettysburg, day one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.56,0:25:24.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,南方会赢的.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.84,0:25:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The South is winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.74,0:25:29.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟踪了汉克,\N拍下了你想要的照片.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.01,0:25:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l followed Hank,\Ngot those pictures you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:42.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你看, 我不知道他在干嘛,\N但我肯定不是什么好事.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, l don't know what he's up to,\Nbut l'm sure it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.03,0:25:44.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我意思是, 我之前从没见过\N这些家伙们,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.32,0:25:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, l've never seen\Nthese guys before,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.86,0:25:47.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们肯定不是从罗特里来的,\N如果你懂我意思的话.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.16,0:25:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're not exactly from the Rotary,\Nif you know what l mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.17,0:25:51.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我喜欢你, 波比.\N- 哦, 我也喜欢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.46,0:25:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l like you, Bobby.\N- Oh, l like you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.04,0:25:53.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要付你多少钱好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.33,0:25:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much am l paying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.88,0:25:58.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们其实还没\N谈论过钱的事呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.13,0:25:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't actually\Ndiscussed money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:01.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 你可以把这当作\N你的第一次加薪.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can consider this\Nyour first raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.58,0:26:06.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 你每天再来,\N我们会谈谈给你一个全职的职位.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.91,0:26:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you come back tomorrow,\Nand we will discuss a full-time position.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.20,0:26:12.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 本.\N我不会让你失望的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.51,0:26:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ben.\Nl won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.14,0:26:30.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝之甘露, 我亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.43,0:26:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nectar of the gods, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.46,0:26:36.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些泡泡.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.77,0:26:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's the bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.91,0:26:44.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}美酒在口.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.18,0:26:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wine comes in at the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.96,0:26:48.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}眼泛爱意.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.22,0:26:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love comes in at the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.27,0:26:55.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我双唇轻啜酒杯,\N我望着你轻叹.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.55,0:26:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I touch my gIass to my Iips,\NI Iook at you and sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.54,0:26:58.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.86,0:26:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Pete.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.28,0:27:00.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抒情.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.56,0:27:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very lyrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.37,0:27:02.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是叶芝的诗.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.67,0:27:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Yeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.60,0:27:05.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一个诗人.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.90,0:27:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a poet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.91,0:27:09.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 我知道.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.20,0:27:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.48,0:27:12.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道还有其他打油诗\N可以用来祝酒的.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.78,0:27:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only other toast l know\Nis a limerick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.18,0:27:15.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 真的. 真的, 皮特, 那是--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.45,0:27:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really. Really, Pete, that was--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.31,0:27:20.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- 曾经有一位女士从戈尔韦来--\N- 乔西!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.58,0:27:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- There once was a Iady from GaIway--\N- Josie!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.68,0:27:28.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是.\N- 现在上开胃菜吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.99,0:27:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes.\N- We'll have our appetizers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.47,0:27:31.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的.\N- 噢, 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.76,0:27:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes.\N- Oh, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.51,0:27:32.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想让你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.80,0:27:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just want you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.99,0:27:37.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你在这个家的地位\N已经改变了,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.30,0:27:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that even though your station\Nin this household has changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.18,0:27:41.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是打算让你\N获得应有的尊重和慈爱.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.47,0:27:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l intend to show you all the respect\Nand affection that you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.53,0:27:48.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你, 凯萨琳.\N我会努力回报的.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.81,0:27:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Catherine.\NAnd l will try to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.93,0:27:51.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 还有戴上你的那顶小小女佣帽吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.25,0:27:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and put on your little maid's cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.86,0:28:01.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳, 难道你不觉得\N你有点难为她了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.16,0:28:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine, don't you think maybe\Nyou're being a little hard on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.56,0:28:04.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我意思是, 她仍是这个家的一分子.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.83,0:28:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l mean, she is still part of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.05,0:28:07.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西要为安德鲁的死负责,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.33,0:28:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie had a hand in Andrew's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.53,0:28:11.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她极尽所能\N要干掉我.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.80,0:28:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she did everything in her power\Nto destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.45,0:28:13.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她没被吊死在树上\N很走运了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.77,0:28:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is lucky she's not hanging\Nfrom a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.93,0:28:17.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.24,0:28:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.50,0:28:20.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西不会的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.81,0:28:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the Josie l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.86,0:28:26.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒想建议为本·荷恩\N被出卖.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.15,0:28:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l would like to propose a toast\Nto Ben Horne's double-cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.74,0:28:29.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为乔西·帕卡的\N卑鄙伎俩.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.02,0:28:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's to Josie Packard's\Ndirty deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.96,0:28:34.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有为坐在这儿打败他们\N的那个女人，喝上一杯.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.26,0:28:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's to the woman\Nwho brought them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.05,0:28:37.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,敬我的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.33,0:28:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.67,0:28:43.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,敬你的, 小贵妇狗.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.97,0:28:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's to you, poodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.21,0:28:50.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,戴安, 我手上正拿着\N一份全国发行的报纸呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.51,0:28:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diane, l'm holding in my hand\Na nationally distributed newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.52,0:28:53.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,走出了我的第一步, 回应\N云顿·厄尔走出的第一步,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.81,0:28:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My opening move, responding\Nto Windom Earle's opening move,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.30,0:28:56.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,按我的指示\N都印在个人专栏上了.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.58,0:28:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was printed in the personal columns\Nper my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.79,0:29:02.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我昨天\N就已经收到他的回应.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.05,0:29:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l've already received\Nhis response to this yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.45,0:29:06.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他早就预料到\N我会怎样回应他了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.72,0:29:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He anticipated my response\Nto his opening move perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.41,0:29:09.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他在耍我, 戴安.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.73,0:29:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's toying with me, Diane.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.24,0:29:15.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道他在哪儿\N和他的计划是什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.53,0:29:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder where he is\Nand what he's planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.52,0:29:20.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,同时,\N我利用这2天没抢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.80,0:29:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile,\Nl've spent the past two days
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.22,0:29:22.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没警章的日子\N去好好的活动了一下身子:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.51,0:29:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without badge and gun\Nthe best way l know how:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.92,0:29:25.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有放松了一下精神.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.21,0:29:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Occupying both body and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.14,0:29:27.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当地的中介商,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.41,0:29:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looked into some real estate,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.84,0:29:31.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,很热情的带我看了\N些有待修葺的房产.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.11,0:29:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what the local agent\Ncharitably refers to as a fixer-upper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.93,0:29:34.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然如此, 那里仍不失为\N一个成家立业,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.22,0:29:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonetheless, it's a place\Nwhere a man might make a home,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.33,0:29:36.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的好地方, 尽管我对过去的事,\N还是耿耿于怀,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.62,0:29:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,raise a family, which is something,\Nin spite of my past,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.77,0:29:38.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望自己仍能面对它.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.06,0:29:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l still hope l'm able to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.95,0:29:42.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然而, 正如这次双峰镇\N发生的命案所显露的,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.26,0:29:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as is the case here\Nin Twin Peaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.08,0:29:46.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,原来这世外桃源里\N也是满布着秘密.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.36,0:29:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even this bucolic hideaway\Nis filled with secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.87,0:29:50.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和我局里的麻烦事\N有关的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.13,0:29:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secrets that may be connected\Nto my trouble at the Bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.66,0:29:53.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在我车里\N发现了可卡因.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.94,0:29:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the cocaine that was found\Nin my automobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.15,0:29:58.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈蒂探员\N会快就会有结论了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:29:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Hardy's deliberations\Nwill soon be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.80,0:30:00.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不能够充分的\N为自己辩护,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.11,0:30:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if l'm not adequately able\Nto defend myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.98,0:30:04.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那很有可能会\N坐牢了.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.28,0:30:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a very real possibility\Nof imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.84,0:30:22.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好, 库珀探员.\N- 欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.10,0:30:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello, Agent Cooper.\N- Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:31.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是给你的. 我偷来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.44,0:30:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you. l stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.51,0:30:35.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得\N把它放回原处更好些吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.81,0:30:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think\Nyou'd better give it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.38,0:30:37.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不,直到你看到里面是什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.68,0:30:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until you look at what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.22,0:30:40.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.48,0:30:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.18,0:30:43.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在这儿发现\N些什么呢, 欧蕊?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.45,0:30:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am l gonna find\Nin here, Audrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.92,0:30:46.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸顾人拍的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.19,0:30:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pictures my father paid for.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.20,0:30:56.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我做的很好吧, 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.50,0:30:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l did good, didn't l?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.20,0:31:00.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 你何止做的好.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.50,0:31:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, you did better than good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.43,0:31:01.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经能救我一命了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.71,0:31:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.17,0:31:04.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.44,0:31:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.92,0:31:10.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那现在我们算是扯平了, 对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.21,0:31:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that makes us even now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.50,0:31:20.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 迪尼斯.\N- 嗨, 库.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.82,0:31:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Denise.\N- Hi, Coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.11,0:31:22.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.43,0:31:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.68,0:31:25.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉, 我不打搅你们吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, am l interrupting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.08,0:31:28.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,特派探员迪尼斯·莱森,\N毒品监察部的.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.36,0:31:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Agent Denise Bryson,\NDrug Enforcement Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.56,0:31:31.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一个非常要好的朋友,\N欧蕊·荷恩.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.83,0:31:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very good friend of mine,\NAudrey Horne.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.48,0:31:35.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,原来他们有女探员?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.74,0:31:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have women agents?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.79,0:31:37.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或多或少吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.07,0:31:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.06,0:31:42.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,欧蕊, 如果你不介意.\N我们有公事要谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.31,0:31:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audrey, if you'll excuse us.\NAgency business.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.54,0:31:44.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你停职了.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.85,0:31:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought you were suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.85,0:31:46.72,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.15,0:31:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.90,0:31:49.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再次感谢. 晚安.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.19,0:31:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.86,0:31:56.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也谢谢你. 别客气.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.16,0:31:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.58,0:32:08.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些照片是在\N一处废旧房那儿拍到的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.87,0:32:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are photographs\Nof an abandoned property
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.71,0:32:10.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就在镇的郊野边上.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.01,0:32:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the outskirts of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.72,0:32:12.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尚·雷诺, 汉克·詹宁斯,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.01,0:32:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean Renault, Hank Jennings,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.03,0:32:16.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,诺玛·詹宁斯的继父,\N还有加拿大的金警官.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.35,0:32:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Norma Jennings' stepfather,\NSergeant King, mounted police.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.29,0:32:18.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们今早\N的活动场面.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.58,0:32:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were at the scene\Nearlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.73,0:32:23.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我在厨房里发现了一道可卡因痕迹\N还有用来稀释它的婴儿泻药.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.02,0:32:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln the kitchen l found traces of cocaine\Nand the baby laxative used to step it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.96,0:32:26.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你把这个,我从农庄那儿取回来的\N和在车上发现的,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.26,0:32:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think if you compare this,\Nwhich was taken from the farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.53,0:32:29.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对比一下,\N你会发现它们是一样的.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.79,0:32:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the stuff found in my automobile,\Nyou'll find it to be a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.53,0:32:31.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是个好消息, 库.\N- 是啊.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.79,0:32:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's good news, Coop.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.71,0:32:34.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在, 我们能讲些\N更重要的事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.03,0:32:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, can we talk about something\Nmore important?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.58,0:32:37.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩到底几岁了?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.90,0:32:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly how old is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.07,0:32:41.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,迪尼斯, 我以为你\N不再对女孩感兴趣了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.37,0:32:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Denise, l would assume\Nyou're no longer interested in girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.42,0:32:44.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,库, 我身穿裙子了,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.71,0:32:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coop, l may be wearing a dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.60,0:32:48.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是有一只小脚脚在中间\N要穿小裤裤的, 如果你懂我意思的话.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.88,0:32:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but l still pull my panties on one leg\Nat a time, if you know what l mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.74,0:32:50.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不太懂.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.01,0:32:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.49,0:33:00.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算把它吃了呢\N还是打算在碟子里一直玩下去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.76,0:33:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna eat that pie\Nor just push it around on my china?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.02,0:33:03.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我不是太饿.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.33,0:33:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess l ain't all that hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.28,0:33:04.68,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想聊聊吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.60,0:33:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.85,0:33:06.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 你不会想听我的\N烦事的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.16,0:33:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't wanna hear\Nmy problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.86,0:33:10.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前无话不谈.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.17,0:33:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to talk about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.17,0:33:14.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在仍是, 艾德.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.44,0:33:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can still talk, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.61,0:33:19.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我们小的时候,\N的那些天大计划吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.91,0:33:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when we were kids,\Nall those plans we made?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.35,0:33:22.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,周围的一切\N似乎都在等着我们去开发,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.61,0:33:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was like we were just waiting around\Nfor our lives to begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.01,0:33:26.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,以为一切都会按着我们所\N计划的那样进行.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.28,0:33:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,planning all that stuff we'd do\Nwhen we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.76,0:33:30.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但生活就是这样,\N总在我们毫无知觉下就开始了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.05,0:33:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, life starts\Nbefore you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.20,0:33:32.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,冷不防, 你就发现人生已经\N过了大半了, 所有的那些计划,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.49,0:33:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, you're halfway through\Nliving it, and all those plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.94,0:33:35.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,都变得毫无意义了.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.26,0:33:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they just don't mean a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.38,0:33:39.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的人生, 诺玛.\N我真不太喜欢这样.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.66,0:33:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my life, Norma.\Nl just don't like it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.44,0:33:49.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是能够做新计划的.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.71,0:33:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can make new plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.82,0:34:07.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安德鲁.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.09,0:34:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.91,0:34:10.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是干嘛, 基巴?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.19,0:34:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Dick?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.87,0:34:12.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能和你说几句吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.16,0:34:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May l have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.01,0:34:15.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,可以.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.30,0:34:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.19,0:34:18.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我觉得我们可能有麻烦了.\N- 什么麻烦?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.47,0:34:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- l feel we may have a problem.\N- What problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.58,0:34:20.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们共同的朋友, 小尼克.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.90,0:34:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's our mutual friend, little Nicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.58,0:34:23.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了?\N- 这我该怎么说才好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.87,0:34:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes?\N- How shall l put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.76,0:34:26.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯, 他, 他...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.04,0:34:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.90,0:34:30.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 我确信那个小尼克,\N它听来似乎不可思议,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.18,0:34:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, l believe that little Nicky,\Nincredible as it may seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.86,0:34:32.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但事实他极有可能是个恶魔.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.15,0:34:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may in fact be the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.82,0:34:34.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.12,0:34:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.09,0:34:38.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,或至少,\N算一级谋杀.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.39,0:34:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or at the very least,\Nhomicidal in the first degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.62,0:34:42.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,安迪, 我们必须的找出\N他父母到底发生了什么事.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.89,0:34:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, we've got to find out\Nwhat happened to his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.54,0:34:50.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经拿到验尸报告了.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.87,0:34:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've got the autopsy report.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.98,0:34:55.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜恩, 杜奇是\N自然死亡的. 心脏病发.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.27,0:34:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dwayne, Dougie died\Nof natural causes. Heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.56,0:34:58.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没有证据证明是谋杀.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.84,0:34:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No evidence of foul play.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.87,0:35:02.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那你有用巫术检查过他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.15,0:35:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you check him for witchcraft?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.27,0:35:08.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不是尸体解剖\N能解释的了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.55,0:35:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the kind of thing\Nthat shows up in an autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.36,0:35:13.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想提出起诉.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.66,0:35:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna press charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.41,0:35:15.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 杜恩, 你是知道的\N如果不是罪案
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.73,0:35:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Dwayne, you know\Nl can't press charges
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.37,0:35:16.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能提出起诉.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.66,0:35:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if there hasn't been a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.81,0:35:20.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好, 就起诉她性谋杀.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.10,0:35:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she killed him with sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.25,0:35:24.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这样足够\N起诉她了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.53,0:35:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how much clearer\Ndoes it have to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.52,0:35:27.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜恩, 今天事儿够多了, 大家都辛苦了.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.80,0:35:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dwayne, it's been a long, hard day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.17,0:35:31.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如你先回家\N好好休息一下吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.47,0:35:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just go home\Nand try and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.18,0:35:33.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你想赶我回家睡觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.48,0:35:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.79,0:35:39.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,决不,除非那个害人精\N被关起来, 罪有应得为止.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.08,0:35:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until that murdering hussy\Nis behind bars, where she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.76,0:35:43.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会以民事诉讼告她的.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.05,0:35:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll sue her, l'll file civil suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.68,0:35:47.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我还剩一口气\N杜奇的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.99,0:35:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll not get her hands\Non any of Dougie's money
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.21,0:35:48.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她就别想染指.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.49,0:35:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as l have a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.99,0:35:53.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一分钱也别想. 啥都没.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.26,0:35:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not one single red cent. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.31,0:35:57.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会... 我会...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.60,0:35:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll... l'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.05,0:36:03.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 那瓶爱尔兰酒\N还在你办公室吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.31,0:36:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, do you still have\Nthat bottle of lrish in your office?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.45,0:36:06.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想放点在热牛奶里\N给妙福的遗孀喝.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.78,0:36:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanna put some in a little warm milk\Nfor the widow Milford.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.20,0:36:13.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 她犹如一把火\N教黑夜燃烧.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.51,0:36:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O, she doth teach the torches\Nto burn bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.21,0:36:16.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她高高在上\N使黑夜黯然
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.52,0:36:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt seems she hangs\Nagainst the cheek of night
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.00,0:36:20.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就像女神伊飞奥耳垂上的璀璨珠宝.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.29,0:36:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like a rich jewel in an Ethiope's ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.00,0:36:27.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,世间珍奇,\N美不胜收.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.29,0:36:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beauty too rich for use,\Nfor earth too dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.98,0:37:02.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,双峰镇警局,\N我是露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.26,0:37:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin Peaks Sheriff Station,\Nthis is Lucy speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.86,0:37:04.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.13,0:37:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.30,0:37:08.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,杜鲁门警长?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.57,0:37:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff Truman?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.52,0:37:11.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,警长?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.81,0:37:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.49,0:37:21.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}杜鲁门警长.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.78,0:37:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff Truman.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.23,0:37:25.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}杜鲁门警长,\N你的电话, 3号线.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.55,0:37:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheriff Truman,\Nyou have a teIephone caII, Iine three.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.51,0:37:32.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.80,0:37:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.25,0:38:00.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,等一下, 后来就好点了.\N然后我说:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.52,0:38:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait, it gets better.\NAnd then l said:
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.73,0:38:04.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,"那好, 那你觉得\N内衣是干嘛用的, 天晓的?"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.03,0:38:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Well, what do you think\Nunderpants are for, anyway?''
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.74,0:38:08.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们再说一个.\N求你了, 再来一个. 一个就好.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.03,0:38:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us another one.\NPlease, another. One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.31,0:38:10.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次, 我有个表兄.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.57,0:38:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one time, l had this cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.14,0:38:13.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他在牛仔比赛\N做中场搞笑秀的, 知道吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.47,0:38:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a clown\Nin this rodeo, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.80,0:38:18.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们那里都是真正的\N高头大马, 懂吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.11,0:38:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just had all these\Nreally big horses, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.98,0:38:22.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们肯定不会相信\N他们都对他做了些什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.28,0:38:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you will not believe\Nwhat they made him do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.25,0:38:23.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么?\N- 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.55,0:38:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.64,0:38:25.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们让他-- 谢谢你.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.95,0:38:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made him-- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.51,0:38:27.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们让他站在中间,\N- 然后.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.78,0:38:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- They made him stand in the middle,\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.82,0:38:31.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后把他的小丑装\N扒个精光.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.09,0:38:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take his clown costume\Ncompletely off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.40,0:39:01.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我能帮你什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.69,0:39:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can l help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.40,0:39:05.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔斯先生, 我并不是\N想给你施加压力.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.65,0:39:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Niles, l don't wanna put\Nthe squeeze on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.84,0:39:07.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经做过牢,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.16,0:39:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been to prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.71,0:39:10.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有些话就不需要我\N说的那么露骨了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.03,0:39:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't need to paint you\Nany pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.90,0:39:14.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.20,0:39:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.42,0:39:19.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,第一条罪名, 你严重违反了\N假释条例.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.70,0:39:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, you're guilty\Nof a serious parole violation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.74,0:39:22.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,光这一条就足够仍你回大牢.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.04,0:39:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough to put you back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.78,0:39:25.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你合作,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.04,0:39:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And unless you cooperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.05,0:39:32.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我会在我的势力范围内\N尽一切可能去保住你.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.31,0:39:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l intend to do everything in my power\Nto make sure you stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.50,0:39:36.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是尔尼·奈尔斯,\N我忏悔.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.82,0:39:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ernie Niles,\Nand l confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.37,0:39:37.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有罪.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.69,0:39:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.81,0:39:41.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我犯下了重罪,\N当然那并不是我的本意.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.12,0:39:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess l'm terribly guilty,\Nagainst my will, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.38,0:39:43.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔斯先生, 我们对你其它的事\N没有兴趣--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.69,0:39:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Niles, we're not really interested\Nin all the--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.64,0:39:45.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们用枪指着我,\N殴打我,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.93,0:39:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They held me at gunpoint,\Nthey beat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.34,0:39:47.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还有暴力\N恐吓我.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.63,0:39:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they threatened me\Nwith physical violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.17,0:39:49.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是简直就是畜牲,\N不得手,他们誓不罢休.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.47,0:39:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These men are animals,\Nthey'll stop at nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.22,0:39:50.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,奈尔斯先生, 只说某--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.50,0:39:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Niles, just--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.44,0:39:51.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要我\N帮他们把毒品分销出去.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.70,0:39:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted me\Nto sell drugs for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.09,0:39:55.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我有试过抵抗的,\N但我的家人就是我的一切.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.37,0:39:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l tried to resist,\Nbut my family means everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.01,0:40:00.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我一家... 他们恐吓我妻子时\N嗯,其实我很懦弱胆小的, 你明白吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.34,0:40:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family... When they threatened\Nmy wife, well, l weakened, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.76,0:40:02.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常, 非常内疚.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.08,0:40:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm terribly, terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.76,0:40:06.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我做错了,但,你理解吗,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.05,0:40:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess l did wrong but, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.20,0:40:09.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爱能让一个人干蠢事,\N你懂吗, 违法犯罪也敢干--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.52,0:40:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,love makes a guy do foolish things,\Nyou know, illegal things--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.08,0:40:12.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尔尼, 尔尼, 尔尼, 你能闭嘴了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.35,0:40:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ernie, Ernie, Ernie, will you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.26,0:40:14.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尔尼先生, 对你所受的\N折磨,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.52,0:40:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Niles, we appreciate the trials\Nyou've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.70,0:40:15.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们深感同情.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.96,0:40:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we sympathize with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.09,0:40:17.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的吗?\N- 所以我们才会出现在这儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.36,0:40:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You do?\N- That's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.87,0:40:19.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦, 是吗?\N- 是的.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.16,0:40:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, you are?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.05,0:40:21.88,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在把你所知道的都一五一十告诉我们.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.33,0:40:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now tell us everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.06,0:40:24.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 是这样的-- 嗯, 他们折磨我,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.37,0:40:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is-- Well, they tortured me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.71,0:40:27.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,事情是这样的,\N他们用卑鄙的, 恐怖的--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.04,0:40:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the thing was,\Nthey did filthy, horrible--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.24,0:40:28.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尔尼先生, 拜托了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.54,0:40:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Niles, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.72,0:40:31.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,只说买毒品有关的部分\N就行了, 请你别囉嗦了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.04,0:40:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the information pertaining\Nto the selling of drugs, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.12,0:40:33.42,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧, 对的.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.41,0:40:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.60,0:40:39.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,对的. 那好, 他们有4公斤\N要卖出去,所以--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.88,0:40:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, they got four kilos\Nof cocaine to sell so--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.09,0:40:41.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他们正急着找买家.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.38,0:40:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're looking for buyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.52,0:40:45.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,于是,为了保护我的家人,\N我就说我能找个买家.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.79,0:40:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So to protect my family,\Nl told them l could find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.57,0:40:46.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.86,0:40:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.92,0:40:50.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你别玩了, 我到哪儿去\N认识这样的人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.26,0:40:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding? l don't know anybody\Nwho would do anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.23,0:40:52.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,现在认识了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.56,0:40:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.85,0:40:56.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个大毒贩\N明天就会到达西雅图.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.13,0:40:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A major drug trafficker\Nwill arrive from Seattle tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.46,0:41:00.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你要在死狗农庄\N为这些人安排一次交易.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.77,0:41:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will set up a meet with these men\Nat the Dead Dog Farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.29,0:41:01.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.61,0:41:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.04,0:41:06.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那我怎么--?\N那我怎么认识他呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.31,0:41:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will l--?\NHow will l know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.74,0:41:09.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你正找他呢,不是吗.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.01,0:41:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.96,0:41:12.49,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他? 他...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.25,0:41:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him? Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.66,0:41:17.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你介意我失陪一下?\N我有神经性膀胱炎.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you excuse me?\Nl've got a nervous bladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.11,0:41:24.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?!\N为什么?! 为什么你会...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.43,0:41:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!\NWhy?! Why would you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.69,0:41:32.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你本来可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.97,0:41:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.80,0:41:47.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她不会出事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.12,0:41:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls she gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.64,0:41:52.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他第一次打她,\N我就发誓会报仇的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.92,0:41:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First time he beat her,\Nl swore revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.21,0:41:55.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,也让他尝尝暴力有多高尚.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.49,0:41:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something violent and noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.56,0:41:57.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但她求我别伤害他,\N还要我保证,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.83,0:41:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She begged me not to hurt him,\Nmade me promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.78,0:42:00.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么这都是为我们俩好.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.06,0:42:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,said it was for both our sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.57,0:42:04.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是4年前的事了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.87,0:42:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.58,0:42:08.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天, 我发誓, 我会杀了他.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.87,0:42:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, l swear, l'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.19,0:42:11.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么代价.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.51,0:42:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.98,0:42:39.20,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,呀, 妈,\N吓死我了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.30,0:42:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Mom,\Ngive me a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.37,0:42:40.89,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.67,0:42:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.11,0:42:44.55,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人乌灯黑火的\N坐那儿干嘛呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.41,0:42:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here\Nsitting alone in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.12,0:42:50.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不干什么. 就坐着而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.41,0:42:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Just sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.35,0:42:54.22,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那, 看看书或干点别的,\N别这样干坐着? 怪吓人的.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.62,0:42:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, read a book or something,\Nwill you? lt's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.80,0:43:04.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,想爸爸了, 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.13,0:43:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's Dad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.24,0:43:06.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他会回来的, 你知道他会的.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.56,0:43:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back, you know he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.55,0:43:09.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不过又是些所谓\N高度机密的玩意儿而已.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.83,0:43:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just some of that\Ntop-secret jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.99,0:43:12.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这次我不敢肯定.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.27,0:43:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not so sure this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.92,0:43:20.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,2周前\N在双食店.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.18,0:43:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was at the Double R\Na couple of weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.44,0:43:25.75,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,爸和我, 聊过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.71,0:43:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad and l, we had this talk
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.93,0:43:29.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,聊了一个他做的梦.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.25,0:43:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about this dream he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.45,0:43:35.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,梦里有一幢白大理石做的豪宅,\N亮着很多灯.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.75,0:43:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was a big house in white marble,\Nlots of lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.42,0:43:40.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那儿, 我也在那儿,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.73,0:43:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was there, and l was there too,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.43,0:43:44.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,过着和谐浑厚,无比愉悦的生活.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.70,0:43:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,living a life of deep harmony and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.18,0:43:48.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那里还有我未来的\N一切.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.44,0:43:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was all this stuff\Nabout my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.53,0:43:51.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一切好事情.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.81,0:43:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.62,0:43:57.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真好. 妈, 真的很棒.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.95,0:43:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of nice. Mom, it was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.07,0:44:01.46,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸\N是个特别的人.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.38,0:44:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father\Nis an extraordinary human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.38,0:44:06.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸\N真真切切是个奇特的怪人.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.69,0:44:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father\Nis a deeply weird individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.69,0:44:10.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但他那顶军帽下\N却是有着过人之处,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.96,0:44:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he has a lot more going on\Nunder his hat than most people,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.00,0:44:12.83,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是肯定的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.26,0:44:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.00,0:44:16.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有时我睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.30,0:44:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes when l'm sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.84,0:44:20.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他会用手指轻轻梳理我的毛发.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.13,0:44:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he runs his fingers through my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.28,0:44:24.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他以为我不知道呢, 但我是知道的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.57,0:44:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks l don't notice, but l do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.17,0:44:37.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我离开多久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.45,0:44:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have l been gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.70,0:44:41.66,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 2天了.\N- 怪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.99,0:44:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Two days.\N- Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.71,0:44:44.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么感觉短多了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.03,0:44:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt seemed much shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.50,0:44:48.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,加兰!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.80,0:44:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garland!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.72,0:44:56.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,波比, 我想你把\N烟灭了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.01,0:44:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobby, l want you\Nto put out that cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.96,0:45:05.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后给我来杯鸡尾酒.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.25,0:45:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then l'd like you to fix me a cocktail.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.66,0:45:08.05,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,要烈的, 如果你不介意的话.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.95,0:45:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong one, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.18,0:45:09.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了, 爸.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.52,0:45:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.07,0:45:19.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.36,0:45:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.25,0:45:22.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.53,0:45:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.69,0:45:24.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不怎么好.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.97,0:45:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly.
